# ==================== HALLS ====================

### Create Hall - Room A
POST {{baseUrl}}/halls
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "venueId": "{{venueId}}",
  "name": "Room A",
  "capacity": 20,
  "isActive": true
}

### Create Hall - Room B
