### Get All Halls
GET {{baseUrl}}/halls
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Halls by Venue
GET {{baseUrl}}/halls?venueId={{venueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Hall By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/halls/{{hallId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update Hall
PUT {{baseUrl}}/halls/{{hallId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Room A - Updated",
  "capacity": 22,
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Hall (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/halls/{{hallId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}